<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="799" height="520" viewBox="0 0 799 520"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="white"/><rect x="24" y="24" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="84" y="45" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13">A</text><rect x="184" y="24" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="244" y="45" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13">B</text><line x1="84" y1="56" x2="84" y2="464" stroke="#555" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="6 4"/><line x1="244" y1="56" x2="244" y2="464" stroke="#555" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="6 4"/><rect x="24" y="200" width="730" height="72" rx="2" ry="2" fill="#eef6ff" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><rect x="24" y="200" width="730" height="22" fill="#ffffff" fill-opacity="0.45" stroke="none"/><line x1="24" y1="222" x2="754" y2="222" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><text x="30" y="214" font-family="monospace" font-size="11" font-weight="600">ref</text><text x="32" y="238" font-family="monospace" font-size="12">External dependency handshake with a very long descriptive line that previously escaped the ref block.</text><text x="32" y="254" font-family="monospace" font-size="12">Return payload includes another long descriptive line to stress multiline measurement.</text><rect x="24" y="320" width="751" height="120" rx="2" ry="2" fill="#fafafa" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><polygon points="24,320 771,320 771,334 765,340 24,340" fill="#fafafa" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><text x="32" y="334" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" font-weight="600">group This group label is intentionally verbose so the container width follows measured content correctly</text><line x1="84" y1="80" x2="244" y2="80" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="244,80 236,75 236,85" fill="#111" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="92" y="72" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace" font-size="12">kickoff</text><line x1="84" y1="360" x2="244" y2="360" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="244,360 236,355 236,365" fill="#111" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="92" y="352" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace" font-size="12">work</text><path d="M24,120 H713 L727 134 V168 H24 Z" fill="#fff8c4" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M713 120 V134 H727" fill="none" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="32" y="140" font-family="monospace" font-size="12">This is a very long yellow note line that should force the container to grow wider than defaults.</text><text x="32" y="156" font-family="monospace" font-size="12">And this second line keeps the multiline height constraints honest.</text><rect x="24" y="464" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="84" y="485" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13">A</text><rect x="184" y="464" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="244" y="485" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13">B</text></svg>
